I"
<h2 id="sass-scss-module-와-styled-components-의-우선순위-조정">sass, scss module 와 styled-components 의 우선순위 조정</h2>

<ul>
  <li>sass 의 css selector 의 우선 순위가 높아서 styled-components 의 style 에 important 를 적용해야 하는 현상이 생겼다</li>
  <li>이유는 sass module 를 가져오는 style tag 가 styled-components 의 style tag 보다 뒤에 위치해서</li>
</ul>

<p>방법은 아래를 링크를 참고 했다</p>

<p>수정 전</p>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">/* commonStyle.module.scss */</span>
<span class="nc">.afterIcon</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nl">color</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">red</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cm">/* useFile.tsx */</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">Button</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">styled</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">button</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">attrs</span><span class="p">(()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">({</span>
    <span class="na">className</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">commonStyle</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">afterIcon</span><span class="p">,</span>
<span class="p">}))</span><span class="s2">`
    color: blue;
}
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>적용한 방법</p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cm">/* useFile.tsx */</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">Button</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">styled</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">button</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">attrs</span><span class="p">(()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">({</span>
    <span class="na">className</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">commonStyle</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">afterIcon</span><span class="p">,</span>
<span class="p">}))</span><span class="s2">`
    &amp;&amp; { // 이렇게 되면 .enyJHo.enyJHo
        color: blue;
    }
}
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p><a href="https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components-website/issues/187">Add “How can I override styles with higher specificity?” to FAQ #187</a></p>
